data.whatILove: Beautiful park like setting - my own garden of Eden!  Flora in bloom February thru November.   Enjoy watching wildlife and their babies - deer, turkeys, fox, raccoons.  50+ hummingbirds visit daily in late spring, 15-20 year round.  Play in the American River, the Bear River or Rollins Lake, all less than 1/2 drive.  Excellent neighborhood with great neighbors.  Join an early morning neighbor walking group.
